1. *Njegov* kućni ljubimci su svi bili srećni. (His pets were all happy.) 
2. *Njegova* majka je bila preplavljena srećom. (His mother was overwhelmed with joy.) 
3. *Njegovom* bratu je bilo mnogo stvari da uradi. (His brother had a lot of things to do.) 
4. *Njegovo* ponašanje je bilo veoma neprijatno. (His behavior was very unpleasant.) 
5. *Njegovi* roditelji nisu znali za njegove planove. (His parents didn't know about his plans.)